title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 29 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 29 2022
description:
Clay and Buck replay Trump's answer to the no-win scenario Pelosi created about traveling to Taiwan. After the foreign policy failures of Afghanistan and Ukraine, has the U.S. ever appeared weaker? Does Joe Biden go to the mat for Taiwan? Los Angeles does a U-turn on mask mandates. What will you tell your grandkids about the mask battles of today? What do the next few months hold for C&B -- and the country?

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
